Cheung Woo-Jin

Introduction

Cherry filter is a 4 membered Korean Co-ed Rock Group under Music Farm. The group consists of Cheung Woo Jin, Tae Head, So Star, and You Been. They were formed in 1997 and are as one of most popular rock group in South Korea.
